Sabi ko patayin mo, off!

134
00:07:39.300 --> 00:07:41.167
- Sandali.
- Patayin mo, sabi ko off!

135
00:07:41.167 --> 00:07:42.567
Off! Off! I-off ito!

136
00:07:42.567 --> 00:07:46.033
Kung patuloy kang sumisigaw, nate-tensyon ako,
