137
00:07:46.033 --> 00:07:48.367
- Ugh, seryoso.
- Ayan.

138
00:07:52.567 --> 00:07:54.767
Kaya, sa kabuuan,

139
00:07:54.767 --> 00:07:59.567
Pagpipilian A, kung saan isang kapanapanabik
dumating ang bagong pag-ibig na may kasamang ale beer,

140
00:07:59.567 --> 00:08:01.767
